						<div class="postbody">You should probably stick with pastebin (you can create multiple pastes if necessary) or use a good file-hosting service like DropBox.
<br />
<br />I haven't looked at the code, but you shouldn't be trying to run code from $0000. Your code should start at $C000 or $8000, depending on the mapper. $0000 is RAM. $8000 to $FFFF is ROM. Your ASM code should .BASE or .ORG accordingly.</div>

